    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king #Imperial/royal_diploma" ref="#people/124"
                            >Fredericus</persName> dei gratia Romanorum <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >rex</rs> augustus. Si antecessorum nostrorum regum et imperatorum pie
                        devotionis limitem prosequentes et circa ecclesias dei opera pietatis
                        exercentes ipsas earumque bona regali potentia a deo nobis concessa
                        conservare ac deffendere studuerimus, id nobis tam ad presentis vite
                        tranquilitatem quam ad eternam beatitudinem promerendam profuturum fore non
                        ambigimus. Quapropter universis Christi regnique nostri fidelibus tam
                        futuris quam presentibus notuum esse volumus, qualiter nos omnipotentis dei
                        causa et ob regni nostri firmam stabilitatem <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">sancti Benedicti</orgName> super
                            <placeName ref="#places/4196">Padum</placeName> situm cum omnibus
                        possessionibus eius, quas nunc habet vel in futuro iuste acquisierit, per
                        hanc <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">mondiburdialem paginam</rs> in
                        tutellam nostre deffenssionis suscipimus. Universa quoque, que eidem
                        monasterio ab antecessoribus nostris <persName>Henrico</persName> videlicet
                        imperatore III° et <persName>Henrico</persName> IIII° parentibus nostris nec
                        non a <persName>Lotario</persName> imperatore seu a dilectissimo patruo
                        nostro et antecessore dive memorie <persName>Conrado</persName> data,
                        concessa et confirmata sunt, imperiali clementia et privilegii nostri
                        auctoritate donamus et confirmarnus. Ad hec ob anime prefati dilecti patrui
                        nostri Conradi perpetuam salutem <rs key="#Mansi">octo mansos</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Villas">villa</rs>, que dicitur <placeName key="#Villas #Mansi"
                            ref="#places/361">Lectus Paludanus</placeName>, sitos, quos ipse eidem
                        monasterio contulit, una cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">braida</rs>
                        cellule <placeName key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/2414"
                            >Gonzagie</placeName> adiacente sancta Benedicto fratribusque ibidem sub
                        regula eius deo militantibus damus et lege in perpetuum valitura
                        confirmamus. Addimus quoque sub attestatione et confirmatione presentis
                        pagine, quicquid Lotharius imperator eidem monasterio in <placeName
                            ref="places/34">Pigugnaga</placeName> contulit. Ut autem hec
                        antecessorum nostrorum et nostra traditio supradicto monasterio in posterum
                        evo rata et inconvulsa permaneant, hanc cartam inde conscribi et sigilli
                        nostri impressione insigniri iussimus edicto regali statuentes, ut, si quis
                        contra hec nostre concessionis seu confirmationis statuta venire
                        presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">centum libras auri</rs>
                        <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere nostre</rs> et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs> compositurus regali banno subiaceat. <rs key="#Witness"
                            >Testes</rs> quoque, in quorum presentia hec facta sunt, <rs
                            key="#Professional_writer">scribi</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notari</rs>
                        fecimus, quorum nomina hec sunt: <persName key="#Abbots #Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma" ref="#people/3787"
                            >Maroquardus</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2478"><placeName
                                key="#Abbots" ref="#places/4421">Fuldensis</placeName></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>, <persName key="#Abbots #Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma" ref="#people/3788"
                            >Henricus</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2479"><placeName
                                key="#Abbots" ref="#places/4422"
                            >Heriffeldensis</placeName></orgName> abbas, magister <persName
                                key="#Notary #Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma">Henricus</persName> notarius,
                        <persName key="#Prevosts #Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma">Conradus</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Prevosts" ref="#places/1609">Vuormatus</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">prepositus</rs>, <persName key="#Count #siblingOf #Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >Gothefridus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> et <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> eius
                        <persName key="#siblingOf #Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma">Poppo</persName>, <persName key="#Count #Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >Otto</persName> [*******] comes iunior, <persName key="#Count #Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >Odalricus</persName> comes de <placeName key="#Count"
                                >Lenzeburchus</placeName>, comes <persName key="#Count #Witness #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                        >Egeno</persName>. Signum domni Frederici Romanorum regis augusti. (M) Ego
                        <persName key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/3789">Arnoldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">canzellarius</rs> vice <persName key="#Archbishops #Archchancellor" ref="#people/3728">Heinrici</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Archbishops" ref="#places/2968">Maguntini</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicanzellarii</rs> recognovi. Data Fulde anno dominice incarnationis
                        M°CLII°, regnante domno Frederico Romanorum rege glorioso, anno vero regni
                        eius I, indictione XV; actum in Christo feliciter. </ab>
                </div>
